\@writefile{lof}{\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {3.4}{\ignorespaces  Posterior distributions of the model parameters for the Per-emb-2 streamer derived from the MCMC point method analysis. The panels show the posterior peak solution, with the corresponding posterior median solution presented in the continued figure. One-dimensional histograms and two-dimensional joint distributions illustrate the parameter constraints and correlations. The solid blue lines mark the locations of the posterior peak and median values, while the dashed black lines indicate the $\pm 34\%$ confidence intervals derived from the posterior distributions. }}{28}{figure.caption.21}\protected@file@percent }
\newlabel{fig:per2_results_cornerplot}{{3.4}{28}{Posterior distributions of the model parameters for the Per-emb-2 streamer derived from the MCMC point method analysis. The panels show the posterior peak solution, with the corresponding posterior median solution presented in the continued figure. One-dimensional histograms and two-dimensional joint distributions illustrate the parameter constraints and correlations. The solid blue lines mark the locations of the posterior peak and median values, while the dashed black lines indicate the $\pm 34\%$ confidence intervals derived from the posterior distributions}{figure.caption.21}{}}
