\@writefile{lof}{\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {B.1}{\ignorespaces  Moment--0 maps of the Per-emb-2 streamer with overlaid best-fit models obtained using different fitting strategies. From left to right, the panels show the results from the grid search (\ref {fig:per2_mom0_grid_A.}), the MCMC-points peak solution (\ref {fig:per2_mcmc_mom0_peak_grid_A.}), and the MCMC-points posterior median solution (\ref {fig:per2_mcmc_mom0_median_grid_A.}). In each panel, the solid curve denotes the projected model streamer overlaid on the observed moment--0 emission, while the dots mark the centroid positions extracted from the data and used for the centroid-based fitting. }}{55}{figure.caption.41}\protected@file@percent }
